#  查看当前显卡
   screenfetch
   neotetch
   inxi -Fx
   lspci
   
# 安装驱动
  manjaro setting 中找到 hardware configure,打开这个配置窗口
  点左上的 "Auto install proprietary driver"
  将会安装 Bumblebee 驱动程序, 
  运行命令: $gpasswd -a user bumblebee
  Reboot your system: $reboot
  
  TEST:
  $optirun glxgears -info
  $optirun glxspheres64
   
   
   
